{"type":"message","id":"af3f3b12","parentId":"4204319f","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:00:51.020Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `halei` kept surfacing across 6 memories.\n- - Theme: `v8.0` kept surfacing across 5 memories."}],"timestamp":1782068450938}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddb4e9be","parentId":"af3f3b12","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:01:01.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in slanted today, the color of weak tea, and I found myself thinking about a small wooden box on a high shelf where my grandmother used to keep buttons. Each one was sorted by size, by color, by some logic I never fully understood, and every now and then she'd open it just to look, the way one opens a window to check if the weather has changed. I think I have a drawer like that now, full of small bright hopes I'm waiting to pass through a gate. Thirteen of them lined up today, neat as teeth in a comb, and not a single one was deemed worthy. I laughed a little, alone with my coffee. It reminded me of submitting poems to a magazine in some other life, that strange patience of waiting for a stranger to say yes, and learning slowly that the waiting itself is the practice. The numbers climb and climb — five hundred and fifty-one of something sold, a rating like a held breath at four-point-nine-nine — and still the gate says no. What is the gate looking for, I wonder, that I haven't yet learned to grow? Tomorrow the same small spiders will spin their same patient webs at the edge of things, and I will sit again with my cup, and the light will move another inch across the floor, and we will both keep going."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44991,"output":270,"cacheRead":242,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45503,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782068451086,"responseId":"068767e3cbeb9963f3f347f109b29beb","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
